库存锁定/扣减/释放的关键条件是什么?请结合mall-common/src/main/java/com/macro/mall/common/config/BaseRedisConfig.java解释触发路径与失败处理。

### Response
【结论】
背景:存在并发控制信号,需关注锁粒度与一致性。

并发控制与锁的实现要点如下:
- 证据显示该段主要关注库存变更。
- 结论:库存锁定/扣减/释放应具备幂等与失败回滚路径,避免不一致。

关键行摘录:
- RedisCacheWriter redisCacheWriter = RedisCacheWriter.nonLockingRedisCacheWriter(redisConnectionFactory);
- return new RedisCacheManager(redisCacheWriter, redisCacheConfiguration);
- return new RedisServiceImpl();

【证据引用】
- mall-common/src/main/java/com/macro/mall/common/config/BaseRedisConfig.java:L53-67(chunk_id=f5c79757902eeaa2)

【原文代码段】
```java
    public RedisCacheManager redisCacheManager(RedisConnectionFactory redisConnectionFactory) {
        RedisCacheWriter redisCacheWriter = RedisCacheWriter.nonLockingRedisCacheWriter(redisConnectionFactory);
        //设置Redis缓存有效期为1天
        RedisCacheConfiguration redisCacheConfiguration = RedisCacheConfiguration.defaultCacheConfig()
                .serializeValuesWith(RedisSerializationContext.SerializationPair.fromSerializer(redisSerializer())).entryTtl(Duration.ofDays(1));
        return new RedisCacheManager(redisCacheWriter, redisCacheConfiguration);
    }


    @Bean
    public RedisService redisService(){
        return new RedisServiceImpl();
    }

}
```

【推理过程】
1. 定位实现点:并发控制与锁
2. 摘录关键行(条件/返回/异常)
3. 围绕库存变更解释业务含义与边界行为

